name: RustyCrypto TRAVIS
description:
:: RUSTYCRYPTOVERSE ::
# 1 RustyCrypto TRAVIS  

The fight for the Greenfluid does not let up and after the fusion with his taxi and weapons he will face his inevitable destiny and will stand as equals with the rest of the rusty-meta-humans who seek to survive no matter what.

Collection: RustyCryptoVerse 

The RustyCryptoVerse is a collection of 101 rust-punk characters, randomly created with the aura of classic pop culture references from the last days on Earth, who are fighting on the epic search of the dominion and understanding of the Mysterious Greenfluid.
